data.description: Fabulous home filled with sunlight and high ceilings, 5 bedrooms and 3 full baths, with granite countertops, stainless steel appliances and beautiful hardwood laminate flooring, first floor guest suite with full bath and open concept living room with fireplace, great for entertaining, the master suite is expansive with two closets and each bedroom is very spacious with walk in closets as well, huge loft area for office or study space for the kids, enjoy the upgraded paver patio, pergola and barn in the backyard. Minutes away from I-65 & access to shopping, restaurants & other services.
